Package: FacileAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Interactive analysis modules for a FacileDataStore
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steve", "Lianoglou", , "lianoglou@dnli.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Denali Therapeutics", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Provides modularized versions of analyses that are commonly
    performed over genomics data. Each analysis module provides an "fplot"
    (facile plot) method that provides an interactive vizualization appropriate
    for an  Rmarkdown document, and an "fxplore" function that launches a
    hyper-interactive version of the analysis using shiny gadgets.
Depends:
    FacileData,
    dplyr,
    plotly
Imports:
    checkmate,
    edgeR,
    matrixStats,
    broom,
    RColorBrewer,
    tidyr
License: Apache Version 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
